snippet.title: Riders of Rohan Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Riders of Rohan™, the new expansion for The Lord of the Rings Online™ is now available!  Clash in Mounted Combat, ride across the plains of Eastern Rohan, and experience Tolkien's beloved story like never before.  Get it today! 

http://rohan.lotro.com/
